---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | n8than.dev" description="About me">
  <section class="container stagger">
    <h1 class="section-heading">About</h1>
    <blockquote class="epigraph">
      "He who has a why to live can bear almost any how."
      <cite>— Friedrich Nietzsche</cite>
    </blockquote>
    <p>
      I'm a developer based in San Diego building web applications that solve real problems for real
      people. I got here the long way around — a CS degree from San Diego State (2020), then a
      pivot into hospital food service at Scripps Mercy during COVID, where running the overnight
      cafeteria alone turned ordering bottlenecks into a problem worth solving.
    </p>
    <p>
      In 2025 I built CafeNightClub, a food ordering system for 80+ hospital staff, and shipped it
      to production. I rebuilt it from scratch as OrderKit to deepen my understanding. AI tooling —
      Claude Code especially — accelerated the process, turning hours of research into minutes of
      focused engineering.
    </p>
    <p>
      Now I'm building on that momentum toward healthcare, infrastructure, and the systems that hold
      communities together. Sympatheia — the idea that we're all connected and responsible for one
      another — is what drives the work.
    </p>

    <blockquote class="epigraph">
      "Accept the things to which fate binds you, and love the people with whom fate brings you together, and do so with all your heart."
      <cite>— Marcus Aurelius</cite>
    </blockquote>

    <section class="skills">
      <h2>Technical Skills</h2>
      <dl>
        <dt>Languages</dt>
        <dd>JavaScript, TypeScript, Python, SQL, HTML, CSS</dd>
        <dt>Frontend</dt>
        <dd>React, Next.js, Astro, Tailwind CSS, SSR, Responsive Design, Accessibility</dd>
        <dt>Backend</dt>
        <dd>Node.js, Bun, PostgreSQL, SQLite, Drizzle ORM, Supabase, Docker, Linux</dd>
        <dt>Tools</dt>
        <dd>Git, GitHub, CI/CD, Vitest, AI-augmented development</dd>
      </dl>
    </section>

    <section class="education">
      <h2>Education</h2>
      <div class="degree">
        <p class="school">San Diego State University</p>
        <p class="program">Bachelor of Science in Computer Science</p>
        <time class="year">2020</time>
      </div>
      <div class="degree">
        <p class="school">Grossmont College</p>
        <p class="program">Associate of Science in Mathematics / Computer Science</p>
        <time class="year">2017</time>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="links">
      <h2>Find me online</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/Nyx000" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sd-nhuse/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        </li>
        <li><a href="mailto:husenathan@gmail.com">Email</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .epigraph {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .epigraph cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .links {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .links h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .links ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .links ul a {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-muted);
    padding: 0.5em 1.25em;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      border-color 0.2s ease,
      color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .links ul a:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .skills {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .skills h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .skills dl {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .skills dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .skills dt:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .skills dd {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0 0;
  }

  .education {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .education h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .degree {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .school {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .program {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .year {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
</style>
